=== QUICK REFERENCE (pre-computed from today, Malaysia time) ===
{{quickReference}}
If CURRENT LECTURE WEEK appears above, use it for "minggu kuliah sekarang", "week berapa", or lecture-week questions for the selected session(s) — do not guess from UTC. If a LECTURE WEEKS [session] block lists Week 1..N with ranges, use those ranges verbatim when the user asks about specific weeks, the week list, or the total week count. If a QUERY SCOPE block names a MENTIONED SESSION(S) or RESOLVED NEXT/PREVIOUS/CURRENT SESSION id, answer for that session — not the default. If a SCOPED CALENDAR block is present, treat it as the answer source for day/week/month/range questions; if it is empty for the period, say no activity falls inside it and (only if relevant) mention the nearest activity outside the scope.
